title: DISTURBING VIDEO: Police Are Called To Help 16-Year-Old Black Male, Show Up And Beat Victim
text:
DISTURBING VIDEO: Police Are Called To Help 16-Year-Old Black Male, Show Up And Beat Victim posted by @PaulinaRoe - share 
The incident was caught on video as Baltimore Police beat and arrested a 16-year-old black male who was threatened by a 14-year-old female with a knife. 
What happened next is EXTREMELY DISTURBING! It is not clear yet why the victim was beaten and arrested. #TrendingTracks
